            <title>[LU-6412] fix typo in lustre.spec.in</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6412</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fix a copy-paste error which it should be zfs rather than ldiskfs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;diff --git a/lustre.spec.in b/lustre.spec.in&lt;br/&gt;
index 5c5fc6d..1210c3c 100644&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;#8212; a/lustre.spec.in&lt;br/&gt;
+++ b/lustre.spec.in&lt;br/&gt;
@@ -196,7 +196,7 @@ backing store of a Lustre server.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; %if %&lt;/p&gt;
{with lustre_utils}
&lt;p&gt; %package osd-zfs-mount&lt;br/&gt;
-Summary: osd-zfs-mount contains mount&apos;s ldiskfs specific dso.&lt;br/&gt;
+Summary: osd-zfs-mount contains mount&apos;s zfs specific dso.&lt;br/&gt;
 Provides: lustre-osd-mount&lt;br/&gt;
 Group: Development/Kernel&lt;/p&gt;</description>
